{"id":427937,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":6}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"392","ytitle":"","mtitle":"在黎明时返航","ftitle":"","authors":["宁宇"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、海上的灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熄灭了，海上的灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨曦托出灯塔的身影；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象漫步祖国大街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮渔轮一夜征程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的光剑护佑我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上人想起在的北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊!夜的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门广场一部分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔灯万盏，号音起伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"网尽星星和明月一轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，黎明的天空庄严升起:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“东方红，太阳升……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、渔轮的友谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔轮出海是一对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔轮归来泊一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缆绳栓两只耳朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叽叽咕咕多亲密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在甲板上散步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听懂她们的私语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸赞渔民的劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍惜战斗的友谊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、护海的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放在水兵结实的肩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面蓝披肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚动几条白浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦!护海的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国门口站岗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋月黑、风高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里面百花、朝阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、在黎明时返航"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明时渔轮返航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心早已进港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市变得亲切又生疏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口音变得生疏又糯香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛向眼睛问好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心扉和心扉叩谈——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发愤是最好的话语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动把生活的意义衡量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答爱人孩子的询问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风风浪浪讲得平常；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪婪地带走所见一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁星下我们又出航!……"}]}